WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:01.334
In "Ancient Returns,"

00:00:01.334 --> 00:00:05.672
we will be adding a series of challenges to the Path of Exile 2 runes for the first time.

00:00:05.672 --> 00:00:07.574
You

00:00:07.574 --> 00:00:10.193
'll earn a piece of the "Adel's Runes" armor set for every two challenges you complete,

00:00:10.193 --> 00:00:11.795
so give it a try!

00:00:12.362 --> 00:00:15.148
To view your current progress and requirements for the challenge,

00:00:15.148 --> 00:00:17.801
simply press "H" to open the challenge interface. There are

00:00:17.951 --> 00:00:19.319
eight challenges in total, and

00:00:19.319 --> 00:00:22.222
their difficulty will gradually increase, from very easy to very difficult.

00:00:22.222 --> 00:00:23.923
To complete the "Rune Seeker" quest,

00:00:23.923 --> 00:00:26.626
you will seek out relics in more and more slots

00:00:26.626 --> 00:00:28.595
and use them to craft new items. The

00:00:29.229 --> 00:00:32.999
seven-slot crafting mode can be quite challenging due to the six waves of monsters,

00:00:32.999 --> 00:00:36.002
so attempting these battles may require some skill.

00:00:38.638 --> 00:00:39.639


00:00:39.639 --> 00:00:41.408
There are many unnecessary leaders within the chapters.

00:00:41.408 --> 00:00:42.959
To complete "The Hunters,"

00:00:42.959 --> 00:00:45.361
you will need to kill six of them. The

00:00:45.361 --> 00:00:49.282
last two, "The Final Thorn - Ekti" and "Sandworm - Enende",

00:00:49.282 --> 00:00:51.551
might be a little hard to find at the Kari Crossroads.

00:00:52.185 --> 00:00:55.271
To track them, simply follow the dried-up riverbed.

00:00:55.388 --> 00:00:57.073
You will find their arena at the very end.

00:00:58.558 --> 00:01:00.877
"Ascended Apostle" requires you to complete the Ascended Trials to

00:01:00.877 --> 00:01:03.880
obtain all eight Ascended class talent points.

00:01:03.880 --> 00:01:06.766
Obtaining the final set of Ascension Points might be a bit challenging.

00:01:06.766 --> 00:01:10.220
You must defeat Zelok in the 4th level of the Trial of Sekma,

00:01:10.653 --> 00:01:14.390
or defeat the Trial Master in the Trial of Chaos after finding all three keys. The

00:01:15.141 --> 00:01:16.960
Chaos Trial

00:01:16.960 --> 00:01:20.029
will take more time because you'll need to run it multiple times,

00:01:20.029 --> 00:01:22.549
but the Skma Trial is generally more challenging,

00:01:22.549 --> 00:01:25.151
so you must choose which one to do.

00:01:26.719 --> 00:01:28.138
"The Apostles" is relatively simple.

00:01:28.138 --> 00:01:30.573
Identify 50 different legendary items. Is

00:01:32.025 --> 00:01:33.910
finding legends painful?

00:01:33.910 --> 00:01:37.647
The map master Jado possesses many abilities that specialize in finding them.

00:01:39.749 --> 00:01:41.151
To complete the "Master Craftsman" quest,

00:01:41.151 --> 00:01:43.720
you will need to use a whole host of different crafting items. All of them

00:01:43.720 --> 00:01:45.839
stemmed from encounters with relics.

00:01:47.240 --> 00:01:48.441
As for the "Cartographer" class,

00:01:48.441 --> 00:01:50.894
you will need to configure your entire map talent tree.

00:01:51.177 --> 00:01:52.712
All 300 points.

00:01:53.163 --> 00:01:56.883
You can complete it by slowly completing all the maps in the fortress.

00:01:56.916 --> 00:01:58.918
But there are other options.

00:01:58.918 --> 00:02:01.054
Each time you defeat the Holy Arbiter,

00:02:01.054 --> 00:02:05.175
you will gain the ability to automatically complete a large portion of the fortress.

00:02:06.676 --> 00:02:09.679
Find the fortress on the map to obtain the key to fight him.

00:02:09.829 --> 00:02:12.832
Each of them has a huge beam of light, making them easily visible even through the mist.

00:02:13.032 --> 00:02:16.719
After fighting him four times, the entire fortress will be completed.

00:02:17.871 --> 00:02:21.040
Last but not least, the “oppressors”.

00:02:21.391 --> 00:02:24.010
This challenge requires defeating three top-tier bosses,

00:02:24.010 --> 00:02:25.478
some of the most difficult battles in the game. The containers of

00:02:25.979 --> 00:02:27.030
Tom Mazu,

00:02:27.030 --> 00:02:28.097
Bodek,

00:02:28.097 --> 00:02:29.682
and Skull Mark.

00:02:30.083 --> 00:02:34.070
These represent the pinnacle of Delirium, Sacrifice, and the Abyss Alliance, respectively.

00:02:34.070 --> 00:02:37.190
Therefore, you must complete the corresponding three task lines before you can complete this challenge.

00:02:37.674 --> 00:02:39.909
Another important thing related to the Skull Mark container

00:02:39.909 --> 00:02:42.162
is that you must defeat him in his fully evolved form.

00:02:42.162 --> 00:02:44.113
This means risking

00:02:44.113 --> 00:02:46.716
returning the finger during the boss fight and still defeating him.

00:02:49.352 --> 00:02:50.303
As I mentioned earlier,

00:02:50.303 --> 00:02:53.223
you will be rewarded with armor set pieces for every two challenges you complete,

00:02:53.223 --> 00:02:55.675
so you can still get some rewards even if you don't complete all the challenges. You can still get some rewards even if you don't complete all the challenges.

00:02:55.675 --> 00:02:58.628
But if you complete it, you will be able to showcase your achievement,

00:02:58.778 --> 00:03:02.715
as everyone on the world channel and forums can see the number of challenges you have completed.

00:03:03.149 --> 00:03:05.835
You will also receive totem decorations from the hideout,

00:03:05.835 --> 00:03:07.837
meaning that from now on, anyone you trade with will

00:03:07.837 --> 00:03:10.840
be able to see that you participated in and defeated that alliance.

00:03:11.191 --> 00:03:15.361
Try these challenges in "Ancient Return," released on May 30th (Taiwan time).

00:03:15.562 --> 00:03:17.463
Thanks for watching, see you then!

